## CONTENT RICHNESS GUIDELINES

### Make it Specific
❌ Generic: "Product Name", "User Name", "Description here"
✅ Specific: "iPhone 15 Pro", "Alex Rivera", "Wireless charging compatible with MagSafe"

### Include Realistic Data
- Prices: $24.99, $1,299, €89.90
- Ratings: 4.7/5, 87%, 9.2/10
- Quantities: 234 in stock, 15 left, sold out
- Dates: "2 hours ago", "March 15, 2024", "Updated yesterday"

### Create Multiple Examples
For listings/grids, provide 3-5 realistic items with variation:
```json
"products": [
  {
    "name": "Nike Air Max 90",
    "price": "$119.95",
    "color": "White/Black",
    "sizes": "7-12 available"
  },
  {
    "name": "Adidas Ultraboost 22",
    "price": "$189.95",
    "color": "Core Black",
    "sizes": "Limited sizes"
  }
]
```

### Add Contextual States
- Loading states: "Loading...", "Syncing data"
- Empty states: "No items found", "Start by adding..."
- Error states: "Connection failed", "Please try again"
- Success states: "Saved!", "Order confirmed"

